{"tid":632383,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(救市)中國人民銀行決定下調部分金融機構存款準備金率以置換中期借貸便利","createTime":"2018-04-17T10:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T17:26:13.000Z","uid":52587,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"9102e90d992f513e46133ae241794d466ada6c98","tid":632383,"uid":52587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:35:42.000Z","msg":"為引導金融機構加大對小微企業的支援力度，增加銀行體系資金的穩定性，優化流動性結構，中國人民銀行決定，從2018年4月25日起，下調大型商業銀行、股份制商業銀行、城市商業銀行、非縣域農村商業銀行、 外資銀行人民幣存款準備金率1個百分點；同日，上述銀行將各自按照「先借先還」的順序，使用降准釋放的資金償還其所借央行的中期借貸便利(MLF)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　中國人民銀行將繼續實施穩健中性的貨幣政策，保持流動性合理穩定，引導貨幣信貸和社會融資規模平穩適度增長，為高品質發展和供給側結構性改革營造適宜的貨幣金融環境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一早就應該咁做啦"},{"pid":"d28400cec83e3341d5abbf931b19b6a43eb921d8","tid":632383,"uid":52587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:36:20.000Z","msg":"睇下夜期90度抽升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日升空READY"},{"pid":"2f545343536080d1c8f36cff5eb90389658a90b2","tid":632383,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"夜期呢下放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5f3bd276a5d16944e9984306a3e9e64ed3635a","tid":632383,"uid":24764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"痴線"},{"pid":"b8e5ce30c70df8ec67bd20202354330d040c2eba","tid":632383,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線"},{"pid":"2fde2b55133cd6da9127579b72f9de1878fa7fba","tid":632383,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"暴力救市"},{"pid":"1737c648d79f1e0f76da6cc086b1e50dbb673bc9","tid":632383,"uid":52587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"呀爺暴力救市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":